{"title":"思念（外一首）——给少时的朋友","authors":["李春华"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"思念（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给少时的朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李春华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当雨季再来的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是否有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨珠串起的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当风儿再次吹落樱花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是否记得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把樱花般的思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别上了胸襟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当海水再次潮起潮落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淹没了一个个足迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是否是否"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还会拾起拾起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那片缀满小星星的馨梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当岁月流成了河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你我站成了两岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才知道思念早已长成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸那不枯的绿柏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在朝阳中呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在黄昏里寻觅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跋涉漫漫黄沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我抚琴低曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——都为了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消失在风里　雨里　泪花里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失落的心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思念便长了脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密密地　密密地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬满了我的身　我的心……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨中的梧桐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那枚梧桐叶吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在茵茵的三月雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地　轻轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你飘进我的心湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打碎一个美人鱼的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我便是那梦中的小水珠呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔柔地　柔柔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融进你那销魂的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你披一件红红的绸衫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是雨后来的吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那桥彩虹被你剪裁了呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你灿然地笑　粲然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我便是那彩虹上的小蝴蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你笑声震颤的乐谱线上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姗姗地　姗姗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与你舞蹈　狂欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会飘走吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如你轻轻地飘来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙娜丽莎的笑缀不成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个圆圆的馨梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此，我担心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这世界便是一座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不老的坟茔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是留下吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿变成那郁郁的梧桐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与你并肩站在这三月的雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}